{"tid":270895,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"9-10月想搵人一齊攀登雲南麗江既哈巴雪山，７日行程表與費用，有冇人JOIN?","createTime":"2017-06-04T15:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T16:45:31.000Z","uid":121126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6314c6032228bd9fcaff5e739bd0ba00b1d8786a","tid":270895,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"其實都係受有位巴打既POST既影響所以想試下登雪山，打第由容易入手先，所以先試入門級雪山,爬過雪山緊係順便去麗江感受下氣氛喇<br />\n<br />\n哈巴雪山，意為「金子之花朵」，主峰海拔 5396 米，為雲南省境內第四高峰<br />\n，因緯度低，氣候相對較溫和，且攀登周期短，岩石地帶沒有太難地形，雪線以上地形簡單，沒有明顯冰裂縫，一直是雲南登山愛好者首選的入門級山峰，稱為「雲南的玉珠峰」<br />\n<br />\n巴哈雪山圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F551.jpg&h=acd06902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/1618075z57cn344t3qici5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F1618075z57cn344t3qici5.jpg&h=6174ebdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/wKgB6lSAjBuAE5aZAAhRYz4QMXI25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2FwKgB6lSAjBuAE5aZAAhRYz4QMXI25.jpg&h=41bfc85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/wKgBpVURHtWAT0sOAAKhozZxlaQ88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2FwKgBpVURHtWAT0sOAAKhozZxlaQ88.jpg&h=0640918e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/DSC06922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2FDSC06922.jpg&h=88b6b344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麗江<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F20